Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\fad(150,150)\pos(640,50)}不需要害怕 try again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何度だって fly away
