Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,完成一件事 有一個東西非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是我缺少的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼阿修拉老師知道得這麼清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,老師還是新月學園學生的時候 夏莉歐告訴她的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,從等級三十提升到五十
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,憤怒的情緒能轉化為最為龐大的魔法能量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,變為黑色精神能量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我缺少的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,缺少的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,難得來到這麼可愛的小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還是忍不住會去想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂的家不是魔法道具店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂 是洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,幾天沒見就長這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣 和之前沒變化啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是亞可嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是蘇西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂寫給我們的信裡老是提到你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,來 快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,先拍張紀念照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,醃鯡魚派
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,每到這個季節 鄰居雅尼阿姨都會給我們做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂 記得明天去謝謝阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我好喜歡這個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,味道好特別 感覺要吃上癮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,還有很多 盡情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可你還要再來一塊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西 我的也給你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這才剛進來不久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是第一次洗三溫暖 我都想永遠留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因為洛蒂家祖祖輩輩都是經營魔法道具店的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為是更古老的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,最近魔法道具銷路不好 就改成報刊亭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這附近就我們一家魔女了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽一直被叫去參加收穫祭 驅魔儀式什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所有地方的魔女數目都在減少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出去 忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂 行行好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我泡澡都只泡三分鐘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可太討厭泡澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,雅尼阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,醃鯡魚派非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不是道謝的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,青苔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,防止綠人症感染的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,綠人症？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,綠人症是這片地區上的疾病 每隔千年有機會爆發一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和群星的方位 人類排出的二氧化碳量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,鯡魚的出生率以及花粉傳播的時機等因素相關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,當各種因素在最壞的情況下重合的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,將醃鯡魚派用最絕妙的溫度烤製就會爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,醃鯡魚派?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦疾病爆發 必須得由當地的魔女阻止傳播
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,感染後會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,身體逐漸被青苔覆蓋 最終枯萎而死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,枯萎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸…媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,本來必須得由洛蒂的媽媽去阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到最先被感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡還有三位魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看 解毒劑的製作方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,製作解毒劑需要五個道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,松樹林裡飄落的雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,被風吹落的漿果葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,薩米人養大的麋鹿的新鮮糞便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,綠色天狗菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,野人製作的傳統藥劑原料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂 有材料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道去哪裡找到它們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道去哪裡找綠色天狗菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西 天狗菇就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是松樹林裡飄落的雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雪不是到處都是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,必須是自然飄落的雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我踢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不是更快嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來是被風吹落的漿果葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,必須是自然吹落的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不能碰它們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,光收集兩個材料就花了那麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要薩米人養大的麋鹿的新鮮糞便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,原來住在這裡的尼可拉斯大叔的家消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,搬家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,人家本來就是遊牧民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,到底去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有手機或信箱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他沒有電話也沒有電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那你以前怎麼聯繫他的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,尼可拉斯大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,回到家說不定就能找到新的聯繫地址的線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…蘇西?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西 喂 蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到連蘇西也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西 蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,蘇西 蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,解毒劑拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在大家枯萎之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,洛蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還剩兩個材料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,必須先找到薩米人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你幫忙找一下帶著麋鹿的薩米人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,兩點鐘方向發現麋鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,別跑 我不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非您就是尼可拉斯大叔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到第四個材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩下野人製作的傳統藥劑原料了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去找野人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,您認識他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在那座山的山腳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,坐這個去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,等我拿到最後一個材料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要藥劑原料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,希望您能幫我製作藥劑原料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,您會幫忙嗎 三十分鐘內能做完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就能製作解毒劑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 您會幫我做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,藥劑原料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,請幫我做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,求您了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 邊角的花紋完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,書上寫了 只有和書上一模一樣的東西才能製作解毒劑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,請重新做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡顏色不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,請求重做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,線有點太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,重做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,從頭開始做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 給我坐那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你說過給我做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你答應過我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有藥劑原料做不了解毒劑 會發生很嚴重的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你解釋過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,做不了的話就早說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是手藝人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,接了任務卻敷衍了事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我說得太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,野人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要是見到他 我會裝死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,野人真沒勁 太差勁了 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這些讓你消沉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以作品也受到了影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在意這種無聊的評價做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,野人先生很帥氣 品味很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是能製作藥劑原料的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定能做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,才能出眾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 天才
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有點大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 得趕緊回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,野人先生 謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在逗我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真慘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,得趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,把行李放下來吧 亞可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,放下行李 讓自己輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就算自己不做 會有人來做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒了你地球照樣轉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,亞可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好辛苦 好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我能忍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,聖…聖誕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,果然它把你丟在那了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 請快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,得令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您 尼可拉斯大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,攪拌所有的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,等顏色變成虹色就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,材料加熱後會馬上凝固
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,必須不斷攪拌直到顏色改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,攪拌棍 攪拌棍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,忍住 必須忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayinab Dyssivyrdd
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,完成一件事 有一個東西非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是你尤其缺少的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayinab Dyssivyrdd
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,完成一件事 耐心非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayinab Dyssivyrdd
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,復…復原了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了洛蒂和蘇西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我才要謝謝你 亞可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩下區區三枚言之葉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就齊了 感覺就像已經找齊了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,區區三枚 隨時 隨時
